<h1>Nested layouts</h1>
<p>
    This page lives at <code>docs/guide/intro</code>. It picks up three
    layout chains in order: root &rarr; <code>docs/</code> &rarr;
    <code>docs/guide/</code>. Each layer contributes its own CSS that is
    collected in outer-to-inner order, so the cascade flows naturally from
    shell &rarr; section &rarr; subsection.
</p>
